/pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html">Deployment</a></p><img src="/2026/06/06/hello-world/%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%9901.png" class="" title="图片2">    # 从伴随目录下找图片<p><img src="建一个自己的博客网站01.png" alt="图片标题" style="zoom:25%"><div class="img-alt is-center">ddddd</div></p><p><img src="/images/hello-world/%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%9903.png" alt="图片"></p><p><img src="/images/helloWorld/%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%9903.png" alt="图片"></p><p><img src="/images/%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%9904.png" alt="图片"></p><p><img src="./建一个自己的博客网站01.png" title="图片标题" alt="没有加载时显示的内容" style="zoom:25%"><div class="img-alt is-center" align="center">图片标题2</div></p>]]>
